metadata.name: Elnaris Phoenix - Adventure
metadata.description: As the ashes of a great war settled, Elnaris emerged, risen from the ashes as a demi-goddess... how on earth did this happen? Follow her as she embarks on a journey through unknown lands, as with each step, she faces treacherous challenges and perilous obstacles in search of her long-lost soul and discovers what happened to her. Join Elnaris on her epic adventure, as she discovers her true powers and changes the course of the land of Escalion forever. Uncover the secrets of a goddess in the making, as she rises to become the first of nine legends across the land!
